1 6. The obligation to provide notice and consider an offer from a group of mobile home
2 owners or a mobile home owners' association applies if the mobile home park owner offers
3 the park for sale or intends to accept an offer to purchase the park at a different price or
4 different terms and conditions; and
5 7. The Maine State Housing Authority, a municipal housing authority, a municipality
6 where the park is located or a nonprofit organization may be assigned the first option to
7 purchase provided to the mobile home owners under the bill.
